Package: dflasso
Title: Decision-Focused Lasso for Predict-Then-Optimize Problems
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Mischa", "Hermans", email = "mischa.hermans@maastrichtuniversity.nl",
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: In predict-then-optimise problems you predict costs from features,
    then optimise. dflasso predicts those costs with a lasso that keeps the
    features which track decision regret, not prediction accuracy, then solves
    the optimisation on new data and measures the regret against an ordinary
    prediction-focused fit.
